Title: Whirlpool — Iconic Stand Mixer
Author: wavelet-director

INT. KITCHEN - MORNING

Close on a hand setting a stainless mixing bowl onto the cast-metal base of a pearl-white stand mixer. The bowl clicks into the locked position.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - MORNING

Macro: the tilt-head of the mixer lowers in a slow arc. The flat beater approaches the surface of the bowl.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - MORNING

Top-down on butter and sugar folding under the paddle. A pale ribbon forms as the beater turns.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - MORNING

Slow push-in on the enamel hip of the mixer. Morning light rakes across the curved cast-metal body. Quiet, sculptural.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - MORNING

Side angle: flour cascades down the inside wall of the bowl, swept into the mix.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - MORNING

Wide hero: the pearl-white mixer alone on a warm walnut counter. Soft morning light from the left. A loaf pan, a single sprig of rosemary nearby.

CUT TO:

INT. STUDIO - DAY

A held still of the mixer on a cream backdrop. The Whirlpool wordmark fades in above. A button reads SHOP THE ICONIC MIXER.

FADE OUT.
